I am just experimenting with Axiom in TeXmacs - more for the nice formatted
output than for anything else, but there is one problem: input and output
aren't numbered.  The input character is just  a little arrow, and there is
no numbering on the output at all.  Can I change this behaviour to include
numbers, so that I can, for example, refer to the output of a previous
command?

Thanks,
Alasdair

