I am trying to write the following (tex expression of)
variable df into a text file.

(20) -> df :=D(exp(x) + 2*x,x);
(20) ->
                                                    
Type: Expression Integer
(21) -> df
(21) ->
$$
{e \sp x}+2
\leqno(21)
$$

                                                    
Type: Expression Integer


I could use the command File(Expression Integer) as
described in 
section 9.24 of the Axiom book. 

